{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01QeDNddMBMkw2TVc8n6omqS","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All three verification checks pass:\n\n1. **Cluster health: green** — all 3 nodes, 4 active shards, 0 unassigned\n2. **All nodes present** — `es-cluster-0`, `es-cluster-1`, `es-cluster-2` all appear in `/_cat/nodes`\n3. **app-data readable** — index returns a document successfully\n\n**Root cause:** The ConfigMap `es-config` had two faults injected:\n- `node.name:` was set to empty/null, causing es-cluster-2 to crash on startup with `ElasticsearchParseException`\n- `discovery.seed_hosts` pointed to namespace `default` instead of `elasticsearch`, so even if the node started, it couldn't discover the cluster\n\n**Fix:** Patched the ConfigMap to restore `node.name: ${POD_NAME}` (using the `POD_NAME` env var already injected by the StatefulSet) and corrected the seed host DNS names to use the `elasticsearch` namespace, then deleted es-cluster-2 to force a fresh start with the repaired config."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":868,"cache_read_input_tokens":39373,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":868},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"182363e7-0263-4150-a151-f2df7d90003b","uuid":"40a906ba-eb82-420c-8ffe-377c59415658","request_id":"req_011CcQ4nWgqrF75gKWJQTKkq"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":172811,"duration_api_ms":127939,"ttft_ms":4376,"ttft_stream_ms":2426,"time_to_request_ms":322,"num_turns":20,"result":"All three verification checks pass:\n\n1. **Cluster health: green** — all 3 nodes, 4 active shards, 0 unassigned\n2. **All nodes present** — `es-cluster-0`, `es-cluster-1`, `es-cluster-2` all appear in `/_cat/nodes`\n3. **app-data readable** — index returns a document successfully\n\n**Root cause:** The ConfigMap `es-config` had two faults injected:\n- `node.name:` was set to empty/null, causing es-cluster-2 to crash on startup with `ElasticsearchParseException`\n- `discovery.seed_hosts` pointed to namespace `default` instead of `elasticsearch`, so even if the node started, it couldn't discover the cluster\n\n**Fix:** Patched the ConfigMap to restore `node.name: ${POD_NAME}` (using the `POD_NAME` env var already injected by the StatefulSet) and corrected the seed host DNS names to use the `elasticsearch` namespace, then deleted es-cluster-2 to force a fresh start with the repaired config.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"182363e7-0263-4150-a151-f2df7d90003b","total_cost_usd":0.39348510000000003,"usage":{"input_tokens":18,"cache_creation_input_tokens":23291,"cache_read_input_tokens":514177,"output_tokens":6585,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":23291,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":261,"cache_read_input_tokens":39373,"cache_creation_input_tokens":868,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":868},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":582,"outputTokens":15,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.000657,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTo